high_descs: Walk across the room and turn left to go to the sink.
Pick up the knife from in front of the tomato.
Go to the left of the sink.
Cut the lettuce on the counter.
Go to the counter to the left of the stove.
Set the knife down on the counter in front of the toaster.
Go back to the counter on the right of the stove.
Pick up a slice of the lettuce from the counter.
Turn around and walk to the refrigerator.
Put the lettuce slice in the refrigerator.  Take the lettuce slice out of the refrigerator.
Turn around and walk across the room to the counter.
Set the lettuce slice on the counter in front of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled slice of lettuce on the counter.

Slice the vegetable with the knife behind the soap

Place the knife down on the counter
Turn right, walk back to the vegetables by the sink
Pick up a slice of the vegetables
Turn right, walk to the fridge behind you
Open the door, place the vegetables in the fridge, close door. After some time, open the door, take the vegetables out, then close the door again
Turn to the right , walk to the counter by the toaster and stove again
Set the vegetables down on the counter
move left to the sink
pick up the knife
